  "prompt": "Can we load money in multi wallet ICICI card?",
  "response": "Yes, you can load money into a multi-wallet ICICI card. Here's a step-by-step guide on how to do it:\n\n1. **Log in to ICICI Net Banking:**\n   - Visit the ICICI Bank website and log in to your net banking account.\n\n2. **Navigate to Card Services:**\n   - Once logged in, go to the 'Cards' section.\n\n3. **Select Multi-Wallet Card:**\n   - Find and select the option for your multi-wallet card.\n\n4. **Load Money:**\n   - Choose the 'Load Money' or 'Add Funds' option.\n   - Select the wallet you want to load money into (e.g., Forex, INR, etc.).\n   - Enter the amount you wish to load.\n\n5. **Confirm Transaction:**\n   - Review the details and confirm the transaction. You may need to enter an OTP (One-Time Password) sent to your registered mobile number.\n\n6. **Transaction Complete:**\n   - Once the transaction is successful, the money will be loaded into the selected wallet of your multi-wallet card.\n\nYou can also load money through the ICICI Bank mobile app by following similar steps. If you encounter any issues, you can contact ICICI Bank customer support for assistance.",
